    public interface ISwcBswSynchronizedTrigger
extends IEntity
    ISwcBswSynchronizedTrigger: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Synchronizes a Trigger provided by a component via a port with a Trigger provided by a BSW module or cluster.
